\pard\nowidctlpar\b0\fs20 1. Our Commitment to You...\par
Acer Inc., of 8/F, No. 88, Sec. 1, Xin Tai 5th Road, Xizhi, New Taipei City 221, and its group of companies around the world (a list of which can be found at {{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK https://www.acer.com/worldwide/ }}{\fldrslt{https://www.acer.com/worldwide/\ul0\cf0}}}}\f0\fs20 ) (collectively, \ldblquote Acer\rdblquote , \ldblquote our\rdblquote  or \ldblquote we\rdblquote ) respect the privacy of our customers and online visitors. \par
